{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2018-11-04/study-hard-delicious-food","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"d4c444cf-54be-568d-b77b-9de0d2691d72","html":"<p>感谢贝妈提供照片(馒头蛋糕)                 </p>\n<p>媒体的力量很强大，从“虎爸虎妈”到“牛蛙计划”，让全民都在关注教育。     </p>\n<p>如果你是父母，你会怎样对待孩子的学习？<br>\n如果你是孩子，你会怎样面对考试与父母的态度？<br>\n如果你是老师，你会为学生们构造一个什么样的“场”？竞赛场？探索场？……    </p>\n<h4>故事1:馒头生日蛋糕</h4>\n<p>贝贝快过5岁生日，由于近期表现不够好，得到的小星星不够多，加上贝贝感冒咳嗽，贝妈不太想给他买奶油生日蛋糕。<br>\n贝妈：贝贝，最近这个月的小星星换不到生日蛋糕，要不，我们自己动手做馒头生日蛋糕。<br>\n贝贝：好啊，好啊，做馒头生日蛋糕。我还想做章鱼型的馒头……    </p>\n<p>章鱼型馒头初型,还有玫瑰花馒头、小猪猪馒头、还有磨牙棒……<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 540px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/09d21/cake1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cake1\"\n        title=\"cake1\"\n        src=\"/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/09d21/cake1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/e07e9/cake1.jpg 200w,\n/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/066f9/cake1.jpg 400w,\n/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/09d21/cake1.jpg 540w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 540px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-